ingredientsDesc:
Vitros Chemistry Products hsCRP Reagent contains:
Reagent 1 (R1): Buffer, bovine serum albumin, polymer, and preservative.
Reagent 2 (R2): Latex particles coated with anti-CRP mouse monoclonal antibodies 0.1% [w/w], buffer and preservative.
Vitros Chemistry Products Calibrator Kit 17 is prepared from stabilized human serum to which human C-reactive protein have been added.
VITROS Chemistry Products hsCRP Performance Verifiers I, II and III are prepared from human plasma and plasma proteins.
Virtros Chemistry Products FS Calibrator 1 is prepared from sodium chloride and processed water.
